<section class="section section--compact" id="qb-toxero-credentials">
  <div class="container container--narrow">
    <header class="section__header">
      <p class="section__eyebrow">Certified by Intuit</p>
      <h2 class="section__heading">Certified QuickBooks ProAdvisor credentials</h2>
      <p class="section__lede">We&rsquo;re Certified QuickBooks ProAdvisors, and we hold no commercial relationship with Xero &mdash; no partner program, no referral fees, no incentive to move you. That&rsquo;s precisely why our read on whether you should switch is worth more than one from a Xero-incentivized firm. Verification available on request.</p>
