      <p class="section__eyebrow">How a QuickBooks-to-Xero engagement works</p>
      <h2 class="section__heading">Honest fit first. Migration only if it&rsquo;s right.</h2>
      <p class="section__lede">The fit assessment is the engagement&rsquo;s most valuable step &mdash; not the migration. If staying on QuickBooks is the answer, we&rsquo;ll say so and credit any scoping deposit toward a QuickBooks engagement instead.</p>
