      <p class="section__lede">The conversion tool itself is often free (Jet Convert covers the current and prior fiscal year); what we price is the professional work around it &mdash; and only if the fit assessment says to switch. If we recommend staying, the assessment fee credits toward a QuickBooks engagement instead. Note that Jet Convert can&rsquo;t be used on files where multi-currency was ever enabled, which is part of why those moves land in the complex tier.</p>
    </header>
