      <p>We&rsquo;re a Certified QuickBooks ProAdvisor firm. We hold no commercial relationship with Xero &mdash; no partner program, no referral fees, no incentive to push you toward either platform. That&rsquo;s precisely what makes our recommendation worth more than one from a firm paid to move you. Every engagement is delivered by a named Certified ProAdvisor with platform-level quality review, and every recommendation is documented so you can take the same read to your accountant for a second opinion if you&rsquo;d like one. We perform the migration and verification and coordinate with your CPA, who files; TechBrot does not provide ongoing Xero bookkeeping, so the engagement ends at a clean handoff.</p>
    </div>
